title: Mega Millions: Got what it takes for Friday's $65M jackpot?
text:
It's time to find out whether that multimillion-dollar dream will come true. Good luck!
Mega Millions had a $65 million jackpot in Friday's drawing. The winning digits: 8, 9, 21, 63, 75
Mega Ball: 14
Megaplier: 4
The multi-state lottery draws numbers on Tuesdays and Fridays. The jackpot starts at $15 million and grows until someone wins.
-- The Oregonian/OregonLive
